%% Debate Loop State Machine
%% Shows all possible states and transitions for the debate loop
%% Covers: FR-004, NFR-004 (convergence guarantee)

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ResolvingDebateMode: Phase 01 starts

    ResolvingDebateMode --> SingleAgentMode: debate_mode = false
    ResolvingDebateMode --> Round1_Creator: debate_mode = true

    SingleAgentMode --> PhaseComplete: Analyst finishes (current behavior)

    Round1_Creator --> Round1_Critic: Creator produces artifacts
    Round1_Critic --> Converged: blocking == 0
    Round1_Critic --> Round1_Refiner: blocking > 0

    Round1_Refiner --> Round2_Critic: Refiner improves artifacts
    Round2_Critic --> Converged: blocking == 0
    Round2_Critic --> Round2_Refiner: blocking > 0, round < 3

    Round2_Refiner --> Round3_Critic: Refiner improves artifacts
    Round3_Critic --> Converged: blocking == 0
    Round3_Critic --> Unconverged: blocking > 0, round == 3 (max)

    Converged --> SaveFinalArtifacts: Save + debate-summary.md
    Unconverged --> SaveBestEffort: Save latest + unconverged warning

    SaveFinalArtifacts --> PhaseComplete
    SaveBestEffort --> PhaseComplete

    PhaseComplete --> [*]: Proceed to GATE-01

    note right of Converged
        Zero BLOCKING findings.
        WARNING findings allowed.
    end note

    note right of Unconverged
        Max 3 rounds reached.
        Save best-effort artifacts.
        Append warning to spec.
    end note
